title: Alex Roy
description: Once again in studio our friend and frequent guest Mr. Alex Roy joins us. This week we cover amature racing,, Miatas, McLarens dinner clubs and a bevy of other random subject matter that usually occur when Alex joins us.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
